name: Toss Boy Toss
description:
This game includes unlock-able character skins, along with a high score and coins to use to unlock the skins!

This is a Fan Game for Jacksepticeye. The game is based on his Animal Crossing: New Horizons series with his character Toss Boy.

Toss Boy Toss's story line:
Help Toss Boy gather as many fruits as possible to help out with the villagers celebration!
